==English==
===Noun===
'''[[pink]] [['un]]'''
#(''chiefly British'') a [[newspaper]] [[supplement]] or [[edition]] concerning [[sport]], especially [[football]]; [[printed]] on pink [[newsprint]]
#*Note: A [[green 'un]] is the same, but is printed on green newsprint.

====Quotations====

*'''1892:''' Doyle, ''The Adventure of the Blue Carbuncle'' — When you see a man with whiskers of that cut and the "Pink 'un" protruding out of his pocket, you can always draw him by a bet.